name: T.E.C.H.N.O.E.Y.E. - B/W DRIFT
description: The electronic eye of digital vision. Looking deep through the elements of a system, of an image. Make the invisible visible. Stimulate the retina. Emulate nature. Create new visual fields. Big bang of the mind. Artwork was made using a Processing generative glitch script and the processed through a buggy software to elevate a synthetic (artifact) glitch with a wild (natural) glitch. Low resolution. High vision. Glitch is the event. Pixel is the element.
